<div id="welcometext"><p><strong>Welcome to the Centre for Retail Research Website, in its 21st year of operation.</strong></p>

<p>The Centre for Retail Research has provided authoritative and expert research and analysis of the retail and service sectors for twenty-one years in Britain, Europe and North America. </p>

<p>We specialise in assessing retail trends across several countries and focus on developments in online shopping, changing consumer behaviour, the changing high/main street and forecasting. We are leaders in the study of retail crime. </p>

